Package com.amazonaws.auth.policy.actions

Collection of actions for AWS access control policies.

See:
          Description

Enum Summary
CloudFormationActions The available AWS access policy actions for AWS Cloud Formation.
S3Actions The available AWS access control policy actions for Amazon S3.
SNSActions The available AWS access control policy actions for Amazon Simple Notification Service.
SQSActions The available AWS access control policy actions for Amazon Simple Queue Service.
 

Package com.amazonaws.auth.policy.actions Description

Collection of actions for AWS access control policies. Actions describe how AWS resources are being accessed or modified when an AWS access control policy is evaluated for an incoming request.
